profile:
WE  PROVIDE   FREE   ON   SITE   ESTIMATES IN THE GTA! 
 
WE PROVIDE TEMP CONTROLLED, SECURE STORAGE, ON MONTH TO MONTH BASES! CUSTOMERS THAT STORE THREE OR MORE MONTHS GET ONE MONTH FREE!!!
WE SELL BOXES, PACKING PAPER, MATTRESS BAGS, BUBBLE WRAP AND MUCH MORE! 
 
At Augusta Movers Toronto Inc., we understand the challenges when it comes to moving whether it is down the street or across the city. Moving your home or business to a new location is exciting but it can be stressful so let Augusta Movers take care of your moving needs and alleviate your anxiety. 
 
Augusta Movers offers a full range of moving, packing and storage solutions to fit your move and budget considerations including discounts for students and seniors. Our expertise in residential and commercial moving, packing and storage has earned us a solid reputation with our customers enabling our business to prosper from repeat business and referrals for local and long distance relocation. Our superior service and attention to all your moving requirements and details, makes us the best choice for your move. 
 
We are experts in what we do from smaller moves, packing and storage for apartment and condo dwellers to houses and commercial relocations of offices, stores, and restaurants. Our unique control and monitoring moving process allows our trained team of professional packers and movers to execute your move hassle-free – we guarantee it.  We believe direct communication is the key to a successful move; we will meet with you to discuss your moving requirements and provide you with a written estimate of the required services with no surprises. 
 
At Augusta Movers Toronto, we are dedicated to providing our customers with quality and fast service at competitive rates.  We are committed to consistently providing excellence in customer service unmatched and beyond industry standards; we will be there for you offering guidance and support from the beginning of your move from packing and storage to transportation of your belongings to your new location. 
 
We encourage you to browse around our site for more information on our moving, packingand storage services. To request a free estimate on your next residential and commercial move, call Augusta Movers Toronto at 416 665 9996.

Residential and Commercial Moving and Storage, Packing and Unpacking Services.

As professional Firefighters, each day we rely on a commitment to teamwork, safety and integrity to provide our communities with emergency services when they need them most.

Applying these same principles to the Residential Moving Industry has allowed us to create a company that provides Ontario with the highest standards of moving and storage services. Why Firemen Movers? We are Safe, Dependable, Hard Working and On-time!

Our commitment to quality working practices ensures that everyone involved in your move is a trained, properly equipped and certified employee. We do not use day labor or contract out, which ensures that we can move your belongings quickly and safely. In addition to exceptionally high service levels we also support 2 important local charities, The Sick Kids Burn Unit, and the Red Door Family Shelter.

Call now to learn more about our Ontario moving services and receive a FREE, no obligation estimate for your move.

profile:
Benini Moving and Storage is a Toronto-based relocation and storage company. Our mission is to provide our clients with the highest quality of service, founded upon the principles of efficiency and reliability. We offer a wide variety of MOVING SERVICES, carefully customized to meet the needs and budget of each client.

To start off, get a FREE ESTIMATE for your move. One of our professional moving managers will contact you with your quote, and answer all your questions. We will even provide you with FREE DELIVERY of all the packing supplies you need.

With Benini, you can relax knowing that your valuables will be handled with the utmost care.
products:
WHAT WE DO

1/ We sign a contract before the job starts with the starting time indicated and the conditions were already discussed with the customer.
2/ We completely wrap the furniture with thick moving blankets to avoid any damages or scratches.
3/ We carefully pack the dishes, glasses and other fragile items with white packing paper.
4/ We take care of pictures and paintings.
5/ We load the truck in a proper way to avoid the furniture shifting and damaging during transportation.
6/We try finding creative solutions to the issues which may occur during the job.
7/ We hoist sofas and other heavy pieces through a balcony if there is no other ways to bring them in.
8/ We conduct our service in a very friendly manner.
9/We work very hard until the job is completed.
services:
WHAT WE DO NOT DO:

1/ We are never late. In fact, we always try to arrive early. 
2/ We do not have “stair” charges.
3/ We do not have ANY hidden charges.
4/ We do not prolong the job deliberately in order to make extra money.
5/ We do not keep our customers’ belongings locked in the truck as a “hostage” while negotiating to get extra payment.
6/ We do not insist to get paid in full before the job is completed.
7/ We do not insist to receive free pizza and beer for lunch.
8/ We do not insist to be tipped even if you are not pleased of our service.
payment_method: Cash, Cheque, Bank draft, E-mail money transfer, Credit Card
name: Benini Moving
